1
00:00:00,810 --> 00:00:02,288
<Please enjoy freely>
Everyone, take a look.

2
00:00:06,189 --> 00:00:07,465
What the...

3
00:00:07,465 --> 00:00:09,373
Doing this kind of things, you people want to ...

4
00:00:09,373 --> 00:00:10,982
Please look at this.

5
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,561
It's not what you think, Domyoji.

6
00:00:16,687 --> 00:00:18,528
Please believe me.

7
00:00:34,407 --> 00:00:37,418
It's just like you've gotten The Red Paper again.

8
00:00:39,626 --> 00:00:43,375
What kind of expression is that?
You've deceived everyone in the school.

9
00:00:43,371 --> 00:00:44,603
It cannot be forgiven.

10
00:00:44,603 --> 00:00:45,814
Get her!

11
00:00:57,735 --> 00:01:01,125
Stop it! Let me go!

12
00:01:04,266 --> 00:01:07,090
You better watch it next time.

13
00:01:19,978 --> 00:01:21,500
Tsukushi-chan.

14
00:01:22,406 --> 00:01:24,444
Sakurako.

15
00:01:25,866 --> 00:01:29,517
You've... finally come back to school.

16
00:01:29,517 --> 00:01:33,667
Don't bother about me. More importantly, are you alright?

17
00:01:36,701 --> 00:01:39,451
It's nothing, just some bruises.

18
00:01:44,947 --> 00:01:47,341
What's with that guy?

19
00:01:49,218 --> 00:01:50,551
That kind of expression...

20
00:01:50,551 --> 00:01:52,165
Please believe me.

21
00:01:55,075 --> 00:01:58,615
Why... won't he believe me?

22
00:02:00,782 --> 00:02:04,833
Tsukushi-chan, let's go look for Domyoji.

23
00:02:06,174 --> 00:02:07,377
Huh?

24
00:02:07,377 --> 00:02:14,708
Once you explain it to him, he'll understand.
Tsukushi-chan isn't that type of person to do such things.

25
00:02:22,371 --> 00:02:23,687
Are you able to stand?

26
00:02:28,436 --> 00:02:30,753
Thanks, Sakurako.

27
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:33,435
I'm fine.

28
00:02:45,589 --> 00:02:48,049
This is really too much.

29
00:02:48,049 --> 00:02:48,934
He's good.

30
00:02:48,934 --> 00:02:54,000
Why is he good? I think the innocent Makino Tsukushi
being capable of such pictures, that's unheard of.

31
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:56,396
What's this guy trying to achieve by doing this?

32
00:02:56,396 --> 00:02:58,187
He must be trying to give himself a challenge.

33
00:02:58,187 --> 00:03:01,357
Like wanting to eat mushrooms which have not
yet been classified as poisonous or edible.
** TL's Note: The mushrooms refer to Tsukushi, the person
eating them is the guy who took slept with her **

34
00:03:04,452 --> 00:03:06,116
Domyoji.

35
00:03:09,843 --> 00:03:14,292
I... That guy... Nothing happened between us.

36
00:03:14,284 --> 00:03:15,853
Please believe me.

37
00:03:15,853 --> 00:03:18,923
With these photos around, how do you expect us to believe you?

38
00:03:18,923 --> 00:03:22,167
Even I myself don't fully understand,
how such a thing can happen without my knowing.

39
00:03:22,163 --> 00:03:24,188
Obviously, you went with that guy to a Hotel,
and together you took those photos.
** TL's Note: It is normal for a couple to rent a Hotel room
for a night, for the sole purpose of having it **

40
00:03:24,188 --> 00:03:28,500
So I'm saying... If anything went on,
I wouldn't have known until I woke up...

41
00:03:28,514 --> 00:03:32,875
Ah... That's not what I meant. That's why... In other words...

42
00:03:32,866 --> 00:03:40,250
Domyoji-san. Please believe Tsukushi-chan.

43
00:03:40,238 --> 00:03:47,000
Even though... From the photos, Tsukushi-chan appears to have
slept with that man in a Hotel.

44
00:03:46,997 --> 00:03:48,630
The photos are undeniably true.

45
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:51,583
But, there's definitely a reason behind it.

46
00:03:51,601 --> 00:03:53,917
Just shut up! I never asked you...

47
00:03:53,937 --> 00:03:55,833
Hey! Sakurako is only helping me explain...

48
00:03:55,833 --> 00:03:57,351
Tsukushi-chan, just keep quiet.

49
00:03:58,147 --> 00:03:58,882
Eh?

50
00:03:58,882 --> 00:04:02,737
Domyoji-san, he's already very hurt by what you've done.

51
00:04:02,737 --> 00:04:07,189
I only hope that the two of you can make up.

52
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:14,578
You have already betrayed me.

53
00:04:15,671 --> 00:04:18,012
Haven't I said this already, it's not how you think it is!

54
00:04:18,012 --> 00:04:21,583
Who's betraying you? I never had a relationship
with you in the first place.

55
00:04:21,591 --> 00:04:24,288
Why do you always say that we do?

56
00:04:31,529 --> 00:04:36,792
Oh yea, then you don't need to be here anymore.

57
00:04:42,316 --> 00:04:48,083
Yea, then I won't need to waste my time, or yours,
here clearing up this misunderstanding.

58
00:04:48,785 --> 00:04:50,503
I'm leaving!

59
00:04:53,785 --> 00:04:58,250
This is so troublesome.
And I thought we could have just resolved it.

60
00:04:58,257 --> 00:05:00,531
Well isn't this actually better?

61
00:05:00,531 --> 00:05:04,517
We now know that Makino isn't serious about
having a relationship with Tsukasa.

62
00:05:10,024 --> 00:05:11,656
What was that...

63
00:05:11,656 --> 00:05:13,746
Makino isn't the type of person to do those things.

64
00:05:13,746 --> 00:05:15,851
It's because you are the only girl in my eyes.

65
00:05:15,851 --> 00:05:20,445
He won't believe me, and yet he says those words.

66
00:05:20,445 --> 00:05:21,611
Ah, it hurts...

67
00:05:34,681 --> 00:05:37,692
Commoners are very used to the cold, so it's all right.

68
00:05:37,692 --> 00:05:40,647
Don't look down on me, I'm just as tough as wild grass.
("Tsukushi" means "wild grass")

69
00:05:45,930 --> 00:05:50,917
Hamburgers... Delicious meals... Wow, great food...

70
00:05:55,387 --> 00:05:56,193
What on earth are those?

71
00:05:56,193 --> 00:06:00,000
Oh! Tsukushi. These photos were taken by Papa. What do you think?

72
00:06:00,003 --> 00:06:02,399
Didn't you notice that the amount has increased?

73
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,925
Papa is such a genius!

74
00:06:04,527 --> 00:06:05,830
Really?

75
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:09,125
Well the next one, shall be our family photo!

76
00:06:09,125 --> 00:06:11,448
Ah, I don't need to be in it.
Just take Mama's photo, that's all.

77
00:06:11,448 --> 00:06:16,750
What are you saying? Shouldn't the four of us
be in the family photo, and not just one person?

78
00:06:16,745 --> 00:06:19,004
This sort of requirement, it's a problem then.

79
00:06:19,004 --> 00:06:21,602
Come on, quickly...

80
00:06:21,602 --> 00:06:24,277
Everyone, smile together!

81
00:06:28,198 --> 00:06:30,091
Obviously, someone has to operate it.

82
00:06:30,729 --> 00:06:31,514
Oh yea...

83
00:06:31,514 --> 00:06:32,875
Tsukushi, you're so smart.

84
00:06:32,875 --> 00:06:35,276
I'll do it...

85
00:06:35,276 --> 00:06:37,166
Really? If you don't mind then...

86
00:06:37,166 --> 00:06:40,226
Come come come come... Everyone, be happy!

87
00:06:41,598 --> 00:06:44,173
Yep, cheese...

88
00:06:49,895 --> 00:06:54,418
There was definitely need to be another person,
who would take this photograph.

89
00:06:54,418 --> 00:06:59,917
I must find the culprit. Sakurako, can you help me out?

90
00:06:59,910 --> 00:07:05,000
Tsukushi-chan, are you doing this for Domyoji-san?

91
00:07:04,981 --> 00:07:06,173
Eh?

92
00:07:06,173 --> 00:07:09,958
Does it matter to you, how he sees you?

93
00:07:09,964 --> 00:07:14,292
He doesn't understand you at all, Tsukushi-chan.

94
00:07:14,298 --> 00:07:19,255
That is why you were so mistreated.

95
00:07:19,255 --> 00:07:21,129
Have you forgotten?

96
00:07:21,129 --> 00:07:23,203
You're right about that, but...

97
00:07:23,203 --> 00:07:27,792
My apologies, if you're doing this for Domyoji, I cannot help you.

98
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:28,950
Eh?

99
00:07:30,303 --> 00:07:34,787
But, no matter what happens,
I'll always be by your side supporting you.

100
00:07:34,787 --> 00:07:37,833
I see, thank you.

101
00:07:37,842 --> 00:07:40,543
Then, I'll contact you again some other time.

102
00:07:40,543 --> 00:07:43,174
Okay, see you.

103
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:51,909
Been seeing you around here a lot.

104
00:07:51,909 --> 00:07:54,937
You even doll up like this, don't be so full of yourself.

105
00:07:54,937 --> 00:08:00,542
I'm sorry, it's not what you think...

106
00:08:01,397 --> 00:08:04,962
Get lost, ugly witches.

107
00:08:05,719 --> 00:08:10,528
It should be considered an offense to see such ugly
people like you hanging out around here.

108
00:08:10,528 --> 00:08:14,313
Quickly get lost, ugly witches!

109
00:08:25,512 --> 00:08:28,933
What's the matter? What happened?

